{"tid":1723531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急需證據] 今朝富輝花園有黑衫人打人想嫁禍示威者","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:19:21.000Z","uid":31205,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"de5a166f0e68c5a10cc48f58ae73ca9bc903b990","tid":1723531,"uid":31205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[代朋友Post]</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今朝馬鞍山富輝花園有黑衫人打人想嫁禍示威者 呼籲附近既泊左車既司機睇下車cam有無影到。</span></strong><br />\n我男朋友家姐同佢爸爸今朝大約10:30-10:40係富輝花園門口接佢個囡既時候比2個黑衫黑褲黑口罩既人打，兇徒事後揸車離開，架車泊係譚仔門口，希望附近既車主可以提供車Cam!!!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">事主已報警，但黑警好大機會會嫁禍話係示威者做</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NU2Jbc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNU2Jbc6.jpg&h=f49248ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有街坊提醒 <br />\n富輝法團好藍。管業處法團李子榮係同一條腸。<br />\n如果係迴旋處位只可以睇吓合一堂影唔影到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyzrTrP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyzrTrP.jpg&h=6375065e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主傷勢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTgRj8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTgRj8V.jpg&h=18a86db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffFZt2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffFZt2g.jpg&h=efb38660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGNkXVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGNkXVB.jpg&h=8bcba9f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JkBFdtX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkBFdtX.jpg&h=3e2fd82c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XOgRj8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOgRj8X.jpg&h=72e6da8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又想屈我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd88cf2b83d8e4b98863e5e0aad6126911841227","tid":1723531,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cc96602894072c3d9c2c06a3e7050d5d5f5c0ec","tid":1723531,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"係時候出示威者宣言"},{"pid":"7d68235f29951e38d88a8d81631f18fdab5ee258","tid":1723531,"uid":31205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:26:19.000Z","msg":"推 希望有車主影到可以提供車CAM"},{"pid":"8a42acffc584dd8f4b42e57e3de18d76520a81de","tid":1723531,"uid":35456,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fcca8a9ba167451e3ec7f022038865628b9e5c2","tid":1723531,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cbe0b2a0d84a24f471c954d3d09268620e2b3fe","tid":1723531,"uid":15747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"推，求cam片"},{"pid":"2f5f6ae094297219e0ddc673925deded408c5fcf","tid":1723531,"uid":92340,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8a42acffc584dd8f4b42e57e3de18d76520a81de","tid":1723531,"uid":35456,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"無端端點會主動去伏普通人呀？<br />\n一係伏狗，一係伏黑社會<br />\n受害者覺得有人想嫁禍，即係都係黃<br />\n黃點會俾自己人伏？"},{"pid":"3e4fa40442249c7c96f81e9f021e927e551b3fd9","tid":1723531,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:45:41.000Z","msg":"同路人咁岩呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［求車cam片］馬鞍山富輝花園被打<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: